    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>(S) In nomine domini nostri Iehsu Christi dei eterni, anno ab incarnatione
                        eius millesimo centesimo quinquagiesimo quarto, pridie idus martii,
                        indictione secunda. Manifesti sumus nos, <persName><name ref="Wido"
                                >Guido</name></persName> filius quondam <persName><name
                                ref="Rusticus">Rustici</name></persName> et <persName><name
                                ref="Marta">Marta</name></persName> iugalis et filia quondam
                                <persName><name ref="Hugo">Ugonis</name></persName> (…) sub notitia
                        duorum propinquorum meorum, nomina quorum subter leguntur, a quibus secundum
                        legem interrogata et cognita sum, (…) nos predicti ambo insimul per hanc
                        cartulam vendimus et tradimus tibi <persName><name ref="Bernardus"
                                >Bernardo</name></persName>, rectori <orgName
                            key="#Rivers #Bridges/pontoons #Hospitals" ref="#juridical_persons/3209"
                                ><rs key="#Hospitals">hospitali</rs> et <rs key="#Bridges/pontoons"
                                >ponti</rs> de <rs key="#Rivers">Arno</rs></orgName>, videlicet
                        integram nostram portionem unius petie terre que est posita infra <rs
                            key="#Village/castle_territory">territoritorio</rs> (sic) de <placeName
                            ref="#places/3221" key="#Rivers #Village/castle_territory"
                            >Massa</placeName>, in loco qui vocatur <placeName ref="#places/3221"
                            >Castellare Merlecti</placeName>. Que tenet unum caput in <rs
                            key="#Rivers">fluvio Iusciane</rs>, aliut caput tenet in terra nostra
                        qui supra iugalibus, latus unum tenet in terra prenominati ponti cum alio
                        lato similiter. Competit exinde nobis medietatem. (…)
                            <foreign>Prezzo</foreign>: argienti denarios lucensis monete soldos
                        quindecim (…). <foreign>Pena</foreign>: in dupplum (…). Quia in tali ordine
                        hanc cartulam <persName key="#Writer #Notary"><name ref="Hubertus"
                                >Ubertum</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Writer #Notary">notarium</rs> scribere rogavimus. Actum in loco
                        qui vocatur <placeName ref="#places/464">Pescia</placeName>. Singna manuum
                        suprascriptorum iugalium, qui comuniter et consentienter hanc cartlam fieri
                        rogaverunt. Singna manuum <persName><name ref="Hugo"
                            >Ugonis</name></persName> filii predicti Guidonis et Ugonis filii et
                                <persName><name ref="Teobaldus">Tebaldi</name></persName> filii
                        quondam Rustici, qui huic cartule interfuerunt. Singna manuum <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Hugolinus">Ugolinelli</name></persName> filii
                        quondam <persName><name ref="Heinricus/Gallenus">Henrichi
                            Galleni</name></persName> et <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Heinricus da Segromigno">Henrichi</name> da <placeName
                                ref="#places/357">Sogremingno</placeName></persName> et <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Rogerius">Rugieri</name></persName> filii
                        quondam <persName><name ref="Belserius da Massa">Belseri</name></persName>
                        da Massa et aliorum plurimum rogatorum <rs key="#Witness">testium</rs>. (S)
                        Hubertus donni inperatoris notarium post traditam complevi et dedi.</ab>
                </div>
